        <![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jS64H5dpmrc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/jS64H5dpmrc/maxresdefault.jpg" /></a></p><br /><p style="clear: both"><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jS64H5dpmrc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/jS64H5dpmrc/0.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jS64H5dpmrc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/jS64H5dpmrc/1.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jS64H5dpmrc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/jS64H5dpmrc/2.jpg" /></a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jS64H5dpmrc"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/jS64H5dpmrc/3.jpg" /></a></p>
<hr style="clear:both" />

<p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><strong># Video starts</strong></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">房間放張床就滿？要兼顧臥室的舒適度與機能性。並在有限空間中收納最多樣的物品。除了要善用櫥櫃家具以外。結合了床架及儲物功能的「收納掀床」。也是相當便利的好選擇。馬上跟著蛙編來看看。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">怎麼使用掀床的收納功能。把空間擠出來！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">本節目感謝小木木業贊助播出。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">本節目感謝壽滿趣收麻吉贊助播出。看下去之前。還沒訂閱的朋友記得先訂閱。並開啟小鈴鐺喔。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">收納掀床這麼多種，要怎麼挑選呢？</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_36.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/jS64H5dpmrc&t=36" target="_blank"><strong># How to choose a storage lift bed?</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">建議先丈量一下房間的大小。以及床的位置擺放。我們這次要示範收納的是。最適合小房間使用。可將床板整個打開。小木木業的貝拉掀床。它採用F1「低甲醛」六分木心板環保綠建材。不但對人體友善，更兼具了環保。女生也能輕鬆抬起，超級省力。選用台灣MIT五金，二段式開關更安心。最讚的是，床板還使用天鵝絨包覆。能有效防止床墊滑動。並能降低煩人的掀床噪音！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">由於不必另外考量抽屜開啟所需的空間範圍。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">即便是租屋處、宿舍等空間狹小的房型。也非常適合使用。我們馬上來看看這樣的標準雙人尺吋床架。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_83.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/jS64H5dpmrc&t=83" target="_blank"><strong># Revelation of bed box storage tips</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">實際可以收納多少物品吧！哇～如果物品都沒分類。直接塞進去床架。視覺看起來雜亂之外。沒有系統性的收納。東西一拿取出來。裡面也是東倒西歪。讓我們好好來規劃整理一下吧！掀床床箱可以視為是一個超大型抽屜。這款貝拉掀床已經區隔好4等份空間。床箱空間大。我們若能利用收納盒、收納袋做分區收納。便能整齊利用空間！我們等會除了會教。棉被及床包的快速折法。及床下收納方式外。其餘物品會使用。無印良品聚丙烯檔案盒當成隔間。有效利用各種零碎的角落。提升收納的效益，小物件不怕凌亂。先來整理這一區的兩用被床包。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_132.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/jS64H5dpmrc&t=132" target="_blank"><strong># The correct way to store quilts</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">通常買回來的床包組都會有收納袋。會建議留下來重覆利用。要特別提醒大家。棉被類尤其是羽絨或蠶絲被。非常不建議用真空收納。因為反覆擠壓後。棉被纖維會容易受損。往後再拿出來使用時。棉被觸感早已回不去原有的蓬鬆及保暖。這也就是為什麼我們在購買棉被時。店家不會用「真空袋」。做為商品包裝的原因之一！這邊建議使用像這種。棉麻材質的棉被收納袋就可以了。將棉被清洗乾淨並除濕完成。就可以摺好收進收納袋啦！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">接著馬上來示範棉被及床包的快速折法。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_175.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/jS64H5dpmrc&t=175" target="_blank"><strong># Quick folding method of quilt \u0026 bed bag</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">先把棉被攤開攤平。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">靠身體這側大慨一個手臂寬。往內折一小部分。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">接著左右兩邊往中間內折後再對折一次。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">之後分三等份並捲起棉被。最後將內折的部分，翻過來包覆棉被。即可完成。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">這樣子的棉被滾來滾去也不會散掉唷！接著準備要來折床包。這時你會發現，不管怎麼折。就是會皺皺的、呈現一個包狀。這是因為床包內側車有一整圈的鬆緊帶。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">整個攤開來。會發現四邊帶有弧度。沒有明顯的直角可以去對折、對襯。只要掌握「角對角」的原則收拾。熟練之後，3分鐘內即可折好。且一個人就能輕鬆完成。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">首先將床包鬆緊帶朝上平放。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">接下來請將A和B這兩個角翻面。塞進上面的C和D這兩個角裡面。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_236.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">梳整一下，將它分成三等份。然後把左側和右側向內折並重疊在一起。床包就會變成長條狀。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後只要把長條狀的床包。分成三等份折起來。就可以收納起來了。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">把棉被和床包都折好後。我們把它們放進日本霜山棉被收納袋。棉麻的日系外型很簡約耐看。袋體用久了不會脆化。有透明視窗可以看到內容物。也有雙提把，橫放直放都可以！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">為了讓衣櫃裡可以有空間擺放當季的衣服。在換季時的冬季或夏季衣物。蛙編都會集中用衣物真空收縮袋收納。放進掀床內。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">今天示範的是蛙編家裡的愛用品。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">壽滿趣收麻吉手捲式真空壓縮袋。袋子材質蠻厚實的，也有雙排氣孔。我們可以先依照衣物大小分尺吋收納。像厚棉外套、厚大衣、毛衣就用Ｌ尺吋的。其它像夏季或小孩衣服就用 Ｍ 或Ｓ尺吋的。像這樣摺好平整的放進去。用滑片封口。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_312.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">接著用雙膝向下壓擠一擠。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">再用手捲一捲就能輕鬆排氣。完全不用吸塵器或真空機。就能把衣物極小極扁化。爭取更多空間。出國旅行、出差時一定要帶個幾片。幫行李箱增加空間，真的很方便！為了讓掀床收納整體視覺統一。不想要有花俏的盒子。像這些收藏品或紀念品。如CD、相片、信紙等物品。可以用無印良品聚丙烯檔案盒。來做分類收納！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">聚丙烯檔案盒之所以。深受整理師、收納達人喜愛。因為它能利用的空間十分多元。放在廚房、浴廁和儲物間都OK。讓視覺看來整齊劃一。下方的圓形孔洞也有助於將盒子拉出。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">現在每一個檔案盒裡都分類收納。不僅方便省時。就算盒子裡東西有點雜亂。但整體看起來還是很整齊。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_367.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/jS64H5dpmrc&t=367" target="_blank"><strong># Storage results Before \u0026 After revealed</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">接下來我們就依序把物品們都擺放進來。先放行李箱、床包棉被、抱枕娃娃。最後是其它物品！收納完成！看起來是不是清爽又舒服。如果我們不放入抱枕娃娃。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">其實裡面還有很多閒置空間。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">可以利用哦！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_385.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/jS64H5dpmrc&t=385" target="_blank"><strong># Instructions for purchasing a storage lift bed</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後。為大家整理收納掀床的選購重點。以及日常維護保養撇步。收納掀床組成結構分別是。床板、置物箱、掀床氣壓棒。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">因為需將床組抬高。並且是靠「氣壓棒」的構造輔助。讓力氣較小的人也能夠輕鬆開啟。因此這邊有幾點要提醒大家特別注意：。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">第一點。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">床板可分為有框及無框2種款式。有框款可避免床墊滑動。無框款則可以增加平時更換床單的便利性。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">第二點。床箱結構要能承受床墊、床架及收納物品的重量。因此，床箱底部的木板厚度。建議選擇六分木心板較為穩固！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">第三點。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">掀床尺寸與氣壓棒應配合床墊重量。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">購買後請告知廠商床墊總重量與尺吋。並且一定要使用安全裝置。如有安全桿、安全扣的五金掀床。最後，大家最容易忽略的掀床板材。建議要挑選低甲醛木材以及水性膠的材料。確保對人體無害而且也較環保。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><p><img src="https://democwise2016.github.io/action-RSS-UT/file-cache/jS64H5dpmrc_456.jpg" /></p></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; "><a href="https://youtu.be/jS64H5dpmrc&t=456" target="_blank"><strong># Tips on daily maintenance of storage lift beds</strong></a></p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">日常保養的部分則建議每月至少打開掀床1～2次。使用除濕機做通風除濕。維持合適的濕度是對木材最好的保養。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">此外。在掀床開啟的同時氣壓棒內的油會有潤滑作用。定期開啟掀床不僅可以保養氣壓棒。還能延長其使用年限哦。看完結合床架及儲物功能的「收納掀床」的總整理。你是不是也對收納掀床有進一步的了解呢？</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">掌握掀床選購的要點。輕鬆買對掀床，讓你睡得安心又舒適。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">收納掀床還能輕鬆幫房間增加收納量！關於房間收納整理。你還有更多好想法嗎？歡迎留言給我們，一起造福大家哦！親愛的蛙粉們，下次見囉！</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">如果你喜歡今天的分享。歡迎點擊下方「超級感謝」。用行動支持我們。做更多實用的影片。也能追蹤IG獲得更多靈感喔。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">最後。</p><p style="max-width: calc(100vw - 1rem);  word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; ">記得鎖定蛙家每週三更新。我們下週見，掰掰～。</p>

<hr style="clear:both" />
====
<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jS64H5dpmrc</p><p>Will the room be full with just one bed? To balance the comfort and functionality of the bedroom and store the most diverse items in a limited space, in addition to making good use of cabinet furniture, a \"storage lift bed\" that combines bed frame and storage functions is also a very convenient and good choice. Follow me now to see how to use the storage function of the lift bed to squeeze out space!</p><p></p><p></p><p>📍Video catalog</p><p>000:00｜Video starts</p><p>00:36｜How to choose a storage lift bed?</p><p>01:23｜Revelation of bed box storage tips</p><p>02:12｜The correct way to store quilts</p><p>02:55｜Quick folding method of quilt \u0026 bed bag</p><p>06:07｜Storage results Before \u0026 After revealed</p><p>06:25｜Instructions for purchasing a storage lift bed</p><p>07:36｜Tips on daily maintenance of storage lift beds</p>]]>
