<p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jS64H5dpmrc</p><p>Will the room be full with just one bed? To balance the comfort and functionality of the bedroom and store the most diverse items in a limited space, in addition to making good use of cabinet furniture, a \"storage lift bed\" that combines bed frame and storage functions is also a very convenient and good choice. Follow me now to see how to use the storage function of the lift bed to squeeze out space!</p><p></p><p></p><p>📍Video catalog</p><p>000:00｜Video starts</p><p>00:36｜How to choose a storage lift bed?</p><p>01:23｜Revelation of bed box storage tips</p><p>02:12｜The correct way to store quilts</p><p>02:55｜Quick folding method of quilt \u0026 bed bag</p><p>06:07｜Storage results Before \u0026 After revealed</p><p>06:25｜Instructions for purchasing a storage lift bed</p><p>07:36｜Tips on daily maintenance of storage lift beds</p>]]></content:encoded>
